name: First Mile Manchert City Prematch Jersey
description: Get your head in the game with the official Manchester City prematch collection – in pieces your favourite players wear to warm up on matchdays. This striking jersey is the perfect way to support the Citizens on the street, at the studio or in the stands. Feel fresh while you train with PUMA's signature dryCELL technology. Stand up for your team and your planet with materials produced in the PUMA x First Mile recycling initiative – turning plastic waste into products and empowering socially disadvantaged people.

description: Lightweight, breathable and cushioned in all the right places, our crew socks are the perfect style for colder days when you need a little extra coverage and a whole lot of comfort.

These socks come in a pack featuring two different classic designs.
specifications: PUMA x TMC logo at ankle

name: individualFINAL Training Soccer Shorts
description: Introducing the next generation of PUMA Soccer: the individualFINAL collection. Designed for the highest level of performance, these shorts use lightweight, breathable, recycled fabrics combined with form-fitting cuts and dryCELL moisture-wicking technology to deliver the ultimate comfort and dominance on the pitch.

name: teamLIGA Training Soccer Shorts
description: PUMA presents perfection on and off the pitch with our teamLIGA collection, a core collection for the style-minded athlete that enjoys the hard-fought battles on the pitch as much as the wins. Our teamLIGA Training Soccer Shorts 2 are the latest iteration of our elite training gear. Equipped with dryCELL technology and made with recycled materials, these shorts will keep you game-ready from head to toe.

name: Tiro Taining Shorts
description: Feel good. Look good. Train better. These adidas soccer shorts are a classic Tiro style and made with the planet in mind. Moisture-absorbing AEROREADY keeps you dry on the training pitch, and zip pockets give you space for essentials.

name: Condivo 22 Training Shorts
description: Created for top-level soccer, these adidas Condivo 22 training shorts are designed to keep you comfortable while you move. Moisture-wicking AEROREADY and mesh 3-Stripes team up so you stay focused through every session. Zip pockets give you somewhere to store your valuables while you concentrate on hitting your goals.

name: Condivo 22 Jersey
description: Created for top-level soccer, this adidas Condivo 22 jersey is all about comfortable movement. Its ventilating mesh side panels are shaped and positioned with male athletes in mind. Working hard to wick moisture from your skin, AEROREADY ensures you're always ready for more.

name: Entrada 22 Graphic Jersey
description: For your team. For your planet. Part of the Entrada 22 range, this adidas jersey puts a new slant on a classic soccer look. Halfway between vertical stripes and horizontal hoops, its diagonal design will keep your teammates standing out on the field. Moisture-wicking AEROREADY ensures your performance matches your appearance.

name: 3-Stripes Hoop OTC Socks
description: Ready for kickoff. These knee-length soccer socks keep you dry on the field with soft, moisture-absorbing fabric. 3-Stripes around the calves show your love for adidas.
specifications: 80% nylon, 13% polyester, 6% natural latex rubber, 1% elastane

name: Utility OTC Socks
description: These supportive knee socks are ideal for any training activity. Made of stretchy fabric that sweeps sweat away from your skin, they include mesh inserts for targeted ventilation. The cushioned footbed offers extra comfort with every step.
specifications: 66% acrylic, 28% polyester, 4% natural latex rubber, 2% elastane
